@flexiarg liberation/noble/right-livelihood
@title Noble Right Livelihood: The Abstaining Faculty Itself
@sigils [💰/天]
@audience practitioners on the path
@tone still
@style liberation-pattern
@path conduct
@tier noble
@references ["liberation/mundane/right-livelihood (prerequisite)" "liberation/noble/right-action (livelihood is sustained action)" "liberation/noble/right-effort (effort enables transition)"]

! conclusion: Not avoiding-wrong-livelihood but the desisting itself — the abstaining, abstinence, and refraining from wrong livelihood operating as factor of path in one intent on the undefiled.

  + context: This operates in one developing the noble path. It is "the desisting, abstaining, abstinence, and refraining from wrong livelihood" — the faculty of livelihood-restraint itself, functioning cleanly.
    + DISTINGUISHING-FROM-MUNDANE:
      Mundane: "I earn by right livelihood" (an I earning)
      Noble: The abstaining faculty operating, intent on the undefiled

    + TRANSCENDENT-QUALITY:
      - Not "I don't engage in wrong livelihood" but clean earning as path-expression
      - Material life that neither grasps at security nor avoids responsibility
      - Livelihood transparent to wisdom
      - Work that is offering rather than acquiring

  + IF:
    Even skillful livelihood involves an earner — one who takes credit for ethical earning, who is proud of avoiding harmful trades. The ethical livelihood can become another source of identity.

  + HOWEVER:
    Material life continues — the question is whether livelihood flows from identification with security or from the path functioning.

    + THE-RUNNING-CIRCLE:
      "Right view, right effort, and right mindfulness keep running and circling around right livelihood" — understanding wrong and right livelihood (view), working to abandon wrong and cultivate right (effort), doing so mindfully.

    + WORN-AWAY:
      "For one of right livelihood, wrong livelihood is worn away. And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong livelihood are worn away."

  + THEN:
    Noble right livelihood is the abstaining faculty operating in context of the path — the natural refraining from wrong livelihood that arises when one is oriented toward liberation rather than security. Not "I earn ethically" but ethical earning as expression of path.

    + NOTE:
      This is the last factor described as encompassed by right view, effort, and mindfulness. The final three (effort, mindfulness, concentration) are self-evidently involved.

  + BECAUSE:
    Livelihood is the most sustained form of action — it shapes daily life hour by hour. When this sustained pattern becomes transparent to path-factors, everyday activity becomes practice.
